nery of $K$-theory, these optical $N$-phases are refined\nfurther to account for the underlying crystalline symmetries of the material,\ngenerating a classification of the topological electromagnetic phase of matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Oct 2021 14:43:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-11"}
